column16: Junior Lake singles on a line drive to left fielder Brandon Barnes.  Kevin Pillar out at home on the throw, left fielder Brandon Barnes to catcher Nick Hundley.
Kevin Pillar doubles (20) on a line drive to center fielder Charlie Blackmon.   Michael Saunders scores.    Russell Martin scores.
Russell Martin singles on a ground ball to center fielder Charlie Blackmon.   Edwin Encarnacion scores.    Michael Saunders to 3rd.
Troy Tulowitzki lines out sharply to right fielder Carlos Gonzalez.
Michael Saunders singles on a ground ball to center fielder Charlie Blackmon.   Edwin Encarnacion to 2nd.
Josh Donaldson grounds out, second baseman Cristhian Adames to first baseman Mark Reynolds.
Devon Travis lines out to second baseman Cristhian Adames.
Ezequiel Carrera doubles (6) on a line drive to right fielder Carlos Gonzalez.   Kevin Pillar scores.
J.  A.   Happ out on a sacrifice bunt, pitcher Yohan Flande to second baseman Cristhian Adames.   Kevin Pillar to 2nd.
Kevin Pillar grounds into a force out, second baseman Cristhian Adames to shortstop Trevor Story.   Russell Martin out at 2nd.    Kevin Pillar to 1st.
Troy Tulowitzki grounds into a double play, third baseman Nolan Arenado to first baseman Mark Reynolds.   Edwin Encarnacion out at 3rd.
Michael Saunders reaches on a force attempt, fielding error by pitcher Yohan Flande.   Josh Donaldson scores.    Edwin Encarnacion to 2nd.
Yohan Flande intentionally walks Edwin Encarnacion.
Josh Donaldson triples (5) on a fly ball to second baseman Cristhian Adames.   J.   Happ scores.    Ezequiel Carrera scores.    Devon Travis scores.
Devon Travis singles on a line drive to left fielder Brandon Barnes.   J.  A.   Happ to 3rd.    Ezequiel Carrera to 2nd.
Chris Herrmann grounds out sharply, second baseman Daniel Descalso to first baseman Mark Reynolds.
Rickie Weeks Jr.   singles on a line drive to right fielder Carlos Gonzalez.
Jake Lamb grounds into a double play, shortstop Trevor Story to first baseman Mark Reynolds.   Paul Goldschmidt out at 2nd.
